text:
1/ How to think about this:

- Who you follow: you control this! Unfollow at any time.

- Power badge: a nice mix of interesting OG Farcaster accounts and newer accounts that have built an audience

- Cast author engagement: discover accounts with engagement worth replies

Should bring back a "pre-permissionless" vibe.

Won't priority mode make it harder for new "good" accounts to get discovered?

TL;DR ‚Äî Yes. But a more tractable problem than classifying all the uninteresting accounts that annoy people.

(Since people don't FAQ links.)

FC idealists and realists sometimes talk past each other. Both see a growing network with 50k DAU. 

Idealists round up to the best possible future. Why isn‚Äôt it more like that today? 

Realists round down to the most probable future: zero, default dead. What can we do today to escape it?

We need both.
Please reply or like the casts of questions you're most interested in hearing
